description: EarthBi is a green earth revolution on the blockchain. We are reinventing how the production of polymers and biodegradable products based on proprietary rights (patents and know-how). Our high-quality products and raw materials can be acquired through the use of our utility token, ERA. EarthBi leverages the blockchain for full transparency and traceability of the production chain to guarantee quality. EarthBi is set to produce 60,000 tons of biopolymers annually.
name: EarthBi
